- You can nu configure voice settings met out opening de voice settings dialog, by using de Synth Settings Ring. de synth settings ring is een group of voice settings you can toggle through by pressing control+NVDA+right en control+NVDA+left. To change een setting use control+NVDA+up en control+NVDA+down.
